column1: Data description: Community weighted mean trait values
Protocols: Community weighted mean trait values were calculated using the FD package in R
Names of data takers: Harrison Lab

Column info: year, site, quadrat, functional richness, functional eveness, functional divergence, functional dispersion, Raup Crick, CWM height, CWM specific leaf area, CWM, leaf area, CWM wet weight, CWM dry weight, CWM leaf water content, CWM, carbon to nitrogen, CWM nitrogen

Definitions & Abbreviations: Fric=functional richness, Feve=functional evenness, Fdiv=functional divergence, Fdis=functional dispersion, RauQ=Raup Crick, CWM=community weighted mean, sla=specific leaf area, area=leaf area, lwc=leaf water content, CN=carbon to nitrogen, N=nitrogen, ag=with annual grasses, noag=no annual grasses
